<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Owen's Web Application</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Owen Kasule Muhereza The code Guru.</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my first web application using Node.js and Express!</p>
        <p>My name is Owen Kasule Muhereza, and I am a student at BYU-Iado University.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero__info">
            <h2>DMC Delorean</h2>
            <ul class="hero__features">
                <li>3 Cup holders</li>
                <li>Superman doors</li>
                <li>Fuzzy dice!</li>
                <li>Flux capacitor ready</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="cta-button">Own Today</button>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__image">
            <img src="/img/delorean.svg" alt="DMC Delorean car">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-columns">
        <section class="upgrades">
            <h2>Delorean Upgrades</h2>
            <div class="upgrades__grid">
                <div class="upgrade-item">
                    <img src="/img/flux-cap.png" alt="Flux Capacitor">
                    <p>Flux Capacitor</p>
                </div>
                <div class="upgrade-item">
                    <img src="/img/flame-decals.png" alt="Flame Decals">
                    <p>Flame Decals</p>
                </div>
                <div class="upgrade-item">
                    <img src="/img/bumper-stickers.png" alt="Bumper Stickers">
                    <p>Bumper Stickers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="upgrade-item">
                    <img src="/img/hub-caps.png" alt="Hub Caps">
                    <p>Hub Caps</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="reviews">
            <h2>DMC Delorean Reviews</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>"So fast its almost like traveling in time." (4/5)</li>
                <li>"Coolest ride on the road." (4/5)</li>
                <li>"I'm feeling McFly!" (5/5)</li>
                <li>"The most futuristic ride of our day." (4.5/5)</li>
                <li>"80's livin and I love it!" (5/5)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Owen Kasule Muhereza. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>